CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Critical Metals Corp is at the forefront of Europe's green energy transition, specializing in the secure and sustainable supply of critical metals and minerals. Our flagship Wolfsberg Lithium Project, located in Austria, is set to become Europe's first fully licensed lithium mine, which positions us to be a leading supplier of lithium in the integrated European battery supply chain. Our expert team, strategic location, and dedication to excellence make us a pivotal player in powering the future of Europe and its partners with clean energy.
